    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "@vvo my use case is:\r\nWhen working with `react-router`, it's a change from `/detail/11` to `/detail/12` (`/detail/:newId:`),\r\nI also have a custom `createConnector` to calculate some derivative values based on `searchResults` and props (in this case, it's `newId`).\r\nBut `getProvidedProps` still receives the old value `11` after the route is changed, then it's this bug.\r\n\r\n",
